node.text:

If there’s any doubt how it went, just check out the cover photo 😂

node.text:
Catching up with @arielleshipe to discuss her wild experience with vertigo - which forced her off social media cold turkey for a little bit

What’s the longest you’ve gone without social media? 

FYI: @despa_valentino ‘s song is Chica Ideal by @sebastianyatra @guaynaa 

_
#wildernessculture

node.title: Boundaries on Social Media and LIVING offline w/Arielle Shipe

node.text:
We are honored to support @UNWorldOceansDay and @Oceanic.Global for World Oceans Day 2020. Our ocean is in a dire state, but solutions do exist. On June 8th, @UnitedNations and @Oceanic.Global are convening leading voices around the world to discuss innovation for a sustainable ocean. Find out how you can become a part of the solution.

This all-digital event is free and open to all online. Learn more & register: UNWorldOceansDay.org/2020

node.title: Join Us At UN World Oceans Day
